{
  "stem": "19518.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they entered Vienna, on the 13th of March '38, two days later they knocked on my uncle's door for the son.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his son knew, and he ran to Czechoslovakia [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] in '38.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when they entered Czechoslovakia, he and another friend chartered a plane to go to Paris, to France.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a snowstorm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he died in this plane crash in the Alps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We read about it in Poland, in 1938, the winter of 1938.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We read it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But meanwhile, they didn't find the son, so they took the father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was in prison in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after six months in prison, they sent him to a concentration camp near Bern.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think-- I don't know what the rest is-- I don't know exactly which little camp it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was like a ghetto, where he tried to explain to me, my uncle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Maybe it was the beginning of Theresienstadt, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] being, my uncle-- my aunt was not the mother of this boy, of the fellow that they were looking for.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they did not take her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And meanwhile her family was-- came from Vienna to the United States.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were working for papers for the two of them to get them out of Austria.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And being she was free to come and go, she arranged the passports and she arranged everything, and he was released, being she proved that there is a passport and there is a visa for him.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they allowed him to leave with the value of-- of $5 worth of thing-- of money, one and the other, nothing else they were allowed to take out.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
